# Capstone CI/CD Project  
**Docker + GitHub Actions + Render**

---

## Project Overview

This is a **full DevOps CI/CD project** where a **Flask backend** and a **static frontend** are containerized using **Docker**, built using **GitHub Actions**, and deployed automatically to **Render** (without using AWS).

---

## Architecture
Developer
|
| git push
v
GitHub Repository
|
| GitHub Actions (CI)
| - Build Docker Images
| - Run checks
v
Render Platform (CD)
|
| Auto Deploy
v
Live Application


---

## Project Structure



capstone-ci-cd/
│
├── .github/workflows/
