│
├── backend/
│ ├── app.py
│ └── Dockerfile
│
├── frontend/
│ ├── index.html
│ └── Dockerfile
│
├── docker-compose.yml
├── .gitignore
└── README.md




## Tech Stack

| Layer        | Technology |
|-------------|------------|
| Backend     | Python, Flask |
| Frontend    | HTML |
| Containers  | Docker |
| CI/CD       | GitHub Actions |
| Deployment  | Render |
| OS          | Linux (CI runner) |

